  "description": "Two sines tuned 5 cents apart create slow underwater beating. Delay and reverb process the dry signal simultaneously — neither muddies the other. The tidal pulse exists in deep space and close quarters at once. Long attack lets the sound emerge like pressure equalising at depth.",
